---
const shots = [
  {
    src: '/5-1024x682.png',
    alt: 'Sky49 amenities gallery image 1',
  },
  {
    src: '/12 (1).png',
    alt: 'Sky49 amenities gallery image 2',
  },
  {
    src: '/4-1024x682.png',
    alt: 'Sky49 amenities gallery image 3',
  },
  {
    src: '/2-1024x682.png',
    alt: 'Sky49 amenities gallery image 4',
  },
] as const;
---

<section id="amenities" class="scroll-mt-24 bg-beige/40 py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-10">
    <div class="mb-10 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-4">
        <div class="h-px w-10 bg-gold" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted">Amenities gallery</p>
      </div>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl text-charcoal md:text-4xl">Amenities at Sky49 Hyderabad</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-muted">
        Editorial references for lifestyle scale—actual Sky49 amenities may vary by tower phase. Confirm the
        latest amenity list and opening sequence during your tour.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed text-muted">
        A 1 lakh+ sq ft amenity footprint is meaningful only when programming matches real usage: weekday
        peak hours, children’s schedules, elder accessibility, and weekend guest traffic. Ask how Sky49
        sequences club openings, staffing, and maintenance budgets—premium living is operational, not merely
        decorative.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      {
        shots.map((img, i) => (
          <figure class="group overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-stone/40 bg-white shadow-sm">
            <img
              src={img.src}
              alt={img.alt}
              class="aspect-[4/3] w-full object-cover transition duration-700 group-hover:scale-[1.03]"
              loading={i < 2 ? 'eager' : 'lazy'}
              decoding="async"
            />
            <figcaption class="sr-only">{img.alt}</figcaption>
          </figure>
        ))
      }
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center">
      <a
        href="#contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-charcoal px-7 py-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white transition hover:bg-gold hover:text-charcoal"
      >
        Register EOI Now
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
